libapache2-mod-rlip for Debian
-----------------------------

  Configuration:

    Apache2.4 module that fixes SERVER_ADDR, REMOTE_ADDR
    then web server is used as backend, behind reverse-proxy,
    the values must be provided by an upstream reverse proxy
    via X-Server-IP, X-Real-IP request headers.

